Package: convertcurr
Type: Package
Title: Updated USD/EUR exchange rate and easy conversion.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anna Alexandra Grigoryan
Maintainer: Anna Alexandra Grigoryan <anna.alexandra.grigoryan@gmail.com>
Description: Looks up the most recent USD/EUR exchange rate via an API call and returns the rate as a number, returns a data.table object on the daily rates for a specified period of time with 2 columns (date and exchange rate), looks up the most recent USD/EUR exchange rate and computes the provided USD amount in EUR (as a number)
